{"tid":1098391,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"彭定康回應佔中案裁決:「令社會極之分裂」","createTime":"2019-04-09T04:40:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-09T15:40:32.000Z","uid":134071,"like":44,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"7bc7dcfa9181196900ef0933c3094c6902ecd0e1","tid":1098391,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T04:40:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190409/59466692\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190409%2F59466692&d=Srnh2QCYUB68P60bIi3tLX6wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=78c6f97d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190409%2F59466692&h=e84c49b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190409/59466692</a><br />\n<br />\n2019年04月09日 <br />\n【佔中案裁決】末代港督彭定康斥當局以過時法例提控分裂社會<br />\n<br />\n佔中案今日裁決，法官陳仲衡裁定佔領運動發起人戴耀廷、陳健民、朱耀明首項串謀作出公眾妨擾罪成，但三人面對的煽惑他人煽惑作出公眾妨擾罪不成立，另有關煽惑他人作出公眾妨擾，則只有朱耀明脫罪。其餘被告全部罪成。末代港督彭定康回應指，當局以過時法例提控，形容裁決令社會極之分裂：「當大部份人都認為香港政府應該團結社會，但政府卻用過時的普通法控罪，尋求報復，起訴發生在2014年的政治事件，看來令社會極之分裂。」（&quot;At a time when most people would have thought that the aim of the Hong Kong Government should be to bring the whole community together it seems appallingly divisive to use anachronistic common law charges in a vengeful pursuit of political events which took place in 2014.&quot;）<br />\n<br />\n德國國會轄下人權及人道救援委員會主席Gyde Jensen亦指，在香港的人權、民主領袖越來越處危險，情況令人驚慌，「我們不能夠接受示威者行使其表達自由與和平集會的權利時，遭受恐嚇。」德國國會議員Martin Patzelt亦譴責政府使用過時和差勁的法例（outdated and bad legislation），去針對提倡民主價值和原則的倡道者，形容有關法例均被聯合國人權委員會嚴重批評，要求中國停止透過特區政府進行政治迫害。"},{"pid":"46de070f9ebeace436bcfcf2e88edeb612aff5ab","tid":1098391,"uid":61280,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T04:44:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我係肥彭一定講埋心底呢句：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n證明我一早預言左，全宇宙支那種係至叻出賣自己人既民瀆！！！！</span></span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13ae1a3ef5be896d9e49a893d37dddbbdfec5b40","tid":1098391,"uid":34334,"like":16,"dislike":5,"score":11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T04:46:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"723917203de41632221111f9c4a941449c6de5b4","tid":1098391,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T04:47:19.000Z","msg":"外父<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"439a1abed16686731493f32b3a90609cde54f9a6","tid":1098391,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T04:58:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"696742444c8a71d300527c455a551f832ae21de2","tid":1098391,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":34,"score":-34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T05:00:12.000Z","msg":"<code>Windows Cortana 留名系統過熱，</code><br />\n<code>請減少負評以便降溫。</code>"},{"pid":"52aa8dc6f00f40fb86972b4f416b9e80eba1aff2","tid":1098391,"uid":6799,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T05:00:56.000Z","msg":"人話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db7025868e9e07442e00070a9c24ca4295dde66e","tid":1098391,"uid":144372,"like":21,"dislike":4,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"13ae1a3ef5be896d9e49a893d37dddbbdfec5b40","tid":1098391,"uid":34334,"like":16,"dislike":5,"score":11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T04:46:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T05:02:11.000Z","msg":"你覺得彭定康可以做乜<br />\n香港其實已經唔係好關佢事<br />\n佢肯出聲你仲想點？"},{"pid":"a189cab21383866e8feb2f32b9fb18509f5607d2","tid":1098391,"uid":152701,"like":4,"dislike":9,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"13ae1a3ef5be896d9e49a893d37dddbbdfec5b40","tid":1098391,"uid":34334,"like":16,"dislike":5,"sco